**Academic Search Tips:**
- Use author name in quotes: `"Smith, J"` or `author:smith`
- Search by DOI when you have it
- Use citation tracking to find related work
- Check if preprints exist on arXiv or SSRN for paywalled papers
- Request papers directly from authors via ResearchGate or email

